{
  "stem": "19218.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Unfortunately, it didn't last long, but we suffered a casualty the first few days of the war.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "My relatives, my cousins, under the name of Gertzek, lived near railroads.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And since the Germans were bombing the railroad tracks-- they lived near the railroad tracks-- they came over to our house, because we lived a little bit away from everything.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And the Polish artillery decided to make a stop about a kilometer away from our-- from our place in a small little mill.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And the German tanks came in, and our home was exactly in their fire lines.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We were all in the house with the shutters closed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We're laying on the floor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And one of the shells, tank shells, went through our home, and it started smoking.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my Uncle Abraham, he ran out of the house, and he was immediately machine gunned by the Germans and he died.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Germans were in town for about maybe five, six days.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And I guess Hitler and Stalin signed the pact where they would divide Poland.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the Germans moved out after a few days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this was around [BACKGROUND NOISE] just before our holiday, which is right now approaching Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As they moved out, I remember we gathered in one of the homes, not in the synagogue, and to recite the prayers.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then somebody came into the house and indicated [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that the Germans are returning.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Didn't know why.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my parents said to me, run to the factory.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The factory was about three miles out of town.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You go there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They remained in the city.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember that night.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We did not have telephone, call each other.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I remember that night.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
